courtorder_explain: The entirety of Catherine Landers 2010-recreating  
myself blog defames my family, is slanderous, and full of lies. We have a  
harassment warrant out for Catherine's arrest (attached) and I will send  
you a copy of the felony stalking warrant as soon as they let us pick up a  
copy. I am also attaching a copy of the protection order (CO212012C000217)  
that was just continued yesterday to be in effect until Feb 17, 2012 at  
which time will be a permanent order. The judge spoke with Catherine via  
phone in court yesterday and ordered her to take down any postings that had  
anything to do with myself or my family, which includes Kyle Wilson, Kevin  
and Justin Landers. Please advise if we need to have the courts get in  
contact with you. Catherine Landers clearly has no desire to obey the  
court. I have reported these blogs and/or videos numerous times through the  
various steps online for privacy violations, some were removed, some not.
